"  About 5 tbsp. olive oil, divided","  About 1 tsp. kosher salt, divided","2 1/2 teaspoons ground sumac*, divided","4  pita breads (6 in. wide)","  Zest of 1/2 lemon","1 teaspoon ground coriander","1/2 teaspoon ground cumin","1 pound medium carrots, peeled and sliced diagonally 1/4 in. thick and 2 to 3 in. long","2 tablespoons butter","1/4 cup golden raisins","1/2 cup very coarsely chopped roasted hazelnuts","1 teaspoon chopped fresh thyme leaves, divided","1 1/2 cups plain whole-milk Greek yogurt","1 tablespoon coarsely chopped flat-leaf parsley"